                    });

            });

            var data ={

            }
            var query=this.jsonToQueryString(data);

            if(next){
                if(this.limit_page==0){
                    return false;
                }
            }
            this.checking = true;
            let key = await this.key();
            var data = {

            }

            var sms = await response.json();

            this.messages =[...this.messages, ...sms.items.messages]
            this.nextPageToken = sms.items.nextPageToken;

            if(next){
                await this.showNext(sms.items.messages);
               
            }
            this.limit_page--;

data-v-678f3534><h2 class="faq__title fade-in" data-v-3bea480e data-v-678f3534>Frequently asked Questions</h2> <div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>How does the service for receiving SMS messages to virtual numbers operate?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>We have our own equipment that holds the SIM cards and our own software that we use to provide mobile numbers to customers to receive messages. When a customer sends a message to an acquired mobile number, it comes to the SIM card. Our software transmits it in the interface of our service.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>What is a virtual number?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>This is an online mobile number that can be used without a SIM card. In our case, it is a mobile number that only belongs to our service for activation using text messages and can only accept incoming messages.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Where can I use my virtual mobile numbers?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Normally, using such mobile numbers for receiving text messages is used to register in social networks (VK, OK, Facebook, Instagram), confirm messengers (Telegram, WhatsApp, Viber, WeChat), and emails (Yandex, Mail.ru, Gmail, Yahoo). They are also used for other websites and services (like Avito, Yula, AUTO.RU, Twitter, SEOsprint, Steam, Uber, Gett, Microsoft, Tinder). Besides, temporary fake mobile numbers may be used for online reception of one-time personal messages so that you can “fly under the radar” and buy no SIM card for one-time use.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Will I be given a SIM card with a virtual number linked to it?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Our service is designed so that you do not have to use a SIM card yourself. You just use the mobile number that you have acquired online without a SIM card. It is displayed in your personal account interface. This interface also displays the text messages sent to this mobile number with activation and confirmation codes.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Will someone access my number when I stop renting it?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Once you received a text message to the virtual mobile number you have acquired, the number is not to sell anymore for the selected website or app. That's why the situation that someone accessed your social network profile or messenger account is absolutely impossible if you use our service. In other words, our individual numbers are "for your eyes only"</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>What is a short-rent mobile number (to receive messages from one website)?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>If you select this tariff, you get a virtual number for a short time from 10 minutes to 1 hour. The exact time depends on the selected country. Short-term rental allows you to receive an unlimited number of SMS messages for the allocated time and only from a single selected website or app.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>What happens if I cannot receive SMS?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>If a message does not arrive at the temporary number you ordered (this can happen for various reasons, for example, the sending site delayed sending or the issued number had a failure), you can close the phone number and order another, money from your balance in this case is not debited will be.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>What can I do if I don't receive a text message?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>If there is no message on the temporary number you have ordered (it may happen for many reasons, for example, the sending website delayed sending or the number has failed), you can deactivate the phone number and the funds will return to the balance so that you can order a new virtual mobile number.</p></div></div><div class="faq-item fade-in" data-v-6e87527c data-v-678f3534><div class="faq-item__head" data-v-6e87527c><p class="medium" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Can I test your service for receiving messages for online activation?</p> <i class="faq-item__icon" data-v-6e87527c></i></div> <div class="faq-item__body" data-v-6e87527c><p class="small" data-v-3bea480e data-v-6e87527c>Sure. To do so, we have a special module with temporary free numbers for one-time text message reception on this webpage. These numbers are public, so they may already be used in some popular services. However, unlike most activation services, we update free numbers every day.</p></div></div> <!----></div></section> <footer class="footer footer--bg" data-v-2759858e data-v-689d7da6><div <script>
  let ApiBase = "https://web.pingme.tel";
  //   let ApiBase = "https://dev-app.pingme.tel";
  let url = window.location.href;
  let did = url.match(/-(\d{6,})\//)[1];
  //   let did = 12252542523;
  async function API(ajax) {
    if (ajax.path) {
      ajax.url = ApiBase + ajax.path;
      delete ajax.path;
    }

    if (!ajax.headers) {
      ajax.headers = {};
    }

    // if (!ajax.headers.Appept) {
    //     ajax.headers.Accept = "application/json"
    // }

    if (
      !ajax.headers["Content-Type"] ||
      ajax.headers["Content-Type"] === "application/json"
    ) {
      // ajax.headers['Content-Type'] = "application/json"
      if (["POST", "PUT"].includes(ajax.method)) {
        //ajax.data.platform = 'pingme'
        ajax.data = JSON.stringify(ajax.data);
      }
    }
    let ret = await jQuery.ajax(ajax);
    return ret;
  }

  let platform = location.href.includes("textr") ? "textr" : "pingme";
  let receiveSMS = new Vue({
    el: "#receiveSMS",
    data: {
      platform,
      number: did,
      captchaData: {},
      messages: [],
      isDataLoading: false,
      notice: "",
      countdown: 0,
    },
    mounted() {
      this.initCaptcha();
      this.setTimer();
    },
    methods: {
      setTimer(reset) {
        clearInterval(this.timer);
        let curTime = Date.parse(new Date());
        if (!reset) {
          let lastTime = localStorage.lastSendTimestamp
            ? JSON.parse(localStorage.lastSendTimestamp)
            : 0;
          if (!lastTime) {
            this.countdown = 0;
          } else {
            let seconds = (curTime - lastTime) / 1000;
            if (seconds < 60 && seconds > 0) {
              this.countdown = 60 - seconds;
            } else {
              this.countdown = 0;
              localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = null;
            }
          }
        } else {
          localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = curTime;
          this.countdown = 60;
        }
        if (this.countdown) {
          this.timer = setInterval(() => {
            if (this.countdown > 0) {
              this.countdown--;
            } else {
              localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = null;
              clearInterval(this.timer);
            }
          }, 1000);
        }
      },
      async getMessages() {
        if (!this.captchaData.token) {
          this.notice = "Please Click the Verification Button first.";
          return;
        }
        this.setTimer(true);
        this.notice = "";
        this.isDataLoading = true;
        try {
          let messageList = await API({
            method: "GET",
            path: "/web/smslist",
            data: {
              month: new Date().toISOString().substr(0, 7),
              number: this.number,
              items: 50,
              page: 1,
              ...this.captchaData,
            },
          });
          if (messageList) {
            messageList.forEach((r) => {
              r.time = new Date(r.time).toLocaleString();
            });
            this.messages = messageList;
            this.isDataLoading = false;
          }
        } catch (e) {
          console.log("e", e);
          if (e.status === 601 || e.status === 403) {
            this.notice = e.responseText;
          }
        } finally {
          this.resetCaptcha();
        }
      },
      initCaptcha() {
        let that = this;
        window.AWSC.use("ic", function (state, module) {
          // 初始化
          window.ic = module.init({

            appkey: "FFFF0N0000000000A4D0",
            // 使用场景标识。它和应用类型标识（appkey字段）一起决定了智能验证的业务场景与后端对应使用的策略模型。您可以在阿里云验证码控制台的配置管理页签找到对应的scene值，请务必正确填写。
            scene: "ic_login",
            // 声明智能验证需要渲染的目标元素ID。
            renderTo: "aliyunCaptcha",
            width: 300,
            height: 56,
            //   language: getBrowserInfo().language.startsWith("zh") ? "cn" : "en",
            language: "en",
            // 验证通过时会触发该回调参数。您可以在该回调参数中将会话ID（sessionId）、签名串（sig）、请求唯一标识（token）字段记录下来，随业务请求一同发送至您的服务端调用验签。
            default_txt: "Click the Button to Verify",
            success_txt: "Verified Successfully",
            fail_txt: "Failed，Click To Refresh",
            scaning_txt: "Smart Check Underway...",
            upLang: {
              cn: {
                //加载状态提示。
                LOADING: "Loading...",
                //等待滑动状态提示。
                SLIDE: "Please Slide to Verify",
                //验证通过状态提示。
                SUCCESS: "Verified Successfully",
                //验证失败触发拦截状态提示。
                ERROR: "Error，Please Try Again",
                //验证失败触发拦截状态提示。
                FAIL: "Failed，Please Try Again",
              },
            },
            success: async function (data) {

                that.notice = "";
              } else {
                that.notice = "Verification error, please try again";
                that.resetCaptcha();
              }
            },
            // 验证失败时触发该回调参数
            fail: function (failCode) {
              that.notice = "Verification fail, please try again";
              that.resetCaptcha();
            },
            // 验证码加载异常时触发该回调参数
            error: function (errorCode) {
              //   that.notice =
              // "Verification failed to load, please refresh the page";
              that.resetCaptcha();
            },
          });
        });
      },
      resetCaptcha() {
        this.captchaData = {};
        window.ic.reset();
      },

Privacy Policy

At Temp Mails, accessible from https://www.temp-mails.com, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Temp Mails and how we use it.

Consent

By using our website, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.

Information we collect

The personal information that you are asked to provide, and the reasons why you are asked to provide it, will be made clear to you at the point we ask you to provide your personal information.

If you contact us directly, we may receive additional information about you such as your name, email address, phone number, the contents of the message and/or attachments you may send us, and any other information you may choose to provide.

How we use your information

We use the information we collect in various ways, including to:

  • Improve, personalize, and expand our website
  • Understand and analyze how you use our website
  • Develop new products, services, features, and functionality

Log Files

Temp Mails follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. All hosting companies do this and a part of hosting services' analytics. The information collected by log files include internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and possibly the number of clicks. These are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable. The purpose of the information is for analyzing trends, administering the site, tracking users' movement on the website, and gathering demographic information.

<script>
  let ApiBase = "https://web.pingme.tel";
  //   let ApiBase = "https://dev-app.pingme.tel";
  let url = window.location.href;
  let did = url.match(/-(\d{6,})\//)[1];
  //   let did = 12252542523;
  async function API(ajax) {
    if (ajax.path) {
      ajax.url = ApiBase + ajax.path;
      delete ajax.path;
    }

    if (!ajax.headers) {
      ajax.headers = {};
    }

    // if (!ajax.headers.Appept) {
    //     ajax.headers.Accept = "application/json"
    // }

    if (
      !ajax.headers["Content-Type"] ||
      ajax.headers["Content-Type"] === "application/json"
    ) {
      // ajax.headers['Content-Type'] = "application/json"
      if (["POST", "PUT"].includes(ajax.method)) {
        //ajax.data.platform = 'pingme'
        ajax.data = JSON.stringify(ajax.data);
      }
    }
    let ret = await jQuery.ajax(ajax);
    return ret;
  }

  let platform = location.href.includes("textr") ? "textr" : "pingme";
  let receiveSMS = new Vue({
    el: "#receiveSMS",
    data: {
      platform,
      number: did,
      captchaData: {},
      messages: [],
      isDataLoading: false,
      notice: "",
      countdown: 0,
    },
    mounted() {
      this.initCaptcha();
      this.setTimer();
    },
    methods: {
      setTimer(reset) {
        clearInterval(this.timer);
        let curTime = Date.parse(new Date());
        if (!reset) {
          let lastTime = localStorage.lastSendTimestamp
            ? JSON.parse(localStorage.lastSendTimestamp)
            : 0;
          if (!lastTime) {
            this.countdown = 0;
          } else {
            let seconds = (curTime - lastTime) / 1000;
            if (seconds < 60 && seconds > 0) {
              this.countdown = 60 - seconds;
            } else {
              this.countdown = 0;
              localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = null;
            }
          }
        } else {
          localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = curTime;
          this.countdown = 60;
        }
        if (this.countdown) {
          this.timer = setInterval(() => {
            if (this.countdown > 0) {
              this.countdown--;
            } else {
              localStorage.lastSendTimestamp = null;
              clearInterval(this.timer);
            }
          }, 1000);
        }
      },
      async getMessages() {
        if (!this.captchaData.token) {
          this.notice = "Please Click the Verification Button first.";
          return;
        }
        this.setTimer(true);
        this.notice = "";
        this.isDataLoading = true;
        try {
          let messageList = await API({
            method: "GET",
            path: "/web/smslist",
            data: {
              month: new Date().toISOString().substr(0, 7),
              number: this.number,
              items: 50,
              page: 1,
              ...this.captchaData,
            },
          });
          if (messageList) {
            messageList.forEach((r) => {
              r.time = new Date(r.time).toLocaleString();
            });
            this.messages = messageList;
            this.isDataLoading = false;
          }
        } catch (e) {
          console.log("e", e);
          if (e.status === 601 || e.status === 403) {
            this.notice = e.responseText;
          }
        } finally {
          this.resetCaptcha();
        }
      },
      initCaptcha() {
        let that = this;
        window.AWSC.use("ic", function (state, module) {
          // 初始化
          window.ic = module.init({
            // 应用类型标识。它和使用场景标识（scene字段）一起决定了智能验证的业务场景与后端对应使用的策略模型。您可以在阿里云验证码控制台的配置管理页签找到对应的appkey字段值，请务必正确填写。
            appkey: "FFFF0N0000000000A4D0",
            // 使用场景标识。它和应用类型标识（appkey字段）一起决定了智能验证的业务场景与后端对应使用的策略模型。您可以在阿里云验证码控制台的配置管理页签找到对应的scene值，请务必正确填写。
            scene: "ic_login",
            // 声明智能验证需要渲染的目标元素ID。
            renderTo: "aliyunCaptcha",
            width: 300,
            height: 56,
            //   language: getBrowserInfo().language.startsWith("zh") ? "cn" : "en",
            language: "en",
            // 验证通过时会触发该回调参数。您可以在该回调参数中将会话ID（sessionId）、签名串（sig）、请求唯一标识（token）字段记录下来，随业务请求一同发送至您的服务端调用验签。
            default_txt: "Click the Button to Verify",
            success_txt: "Verified Successfully",
            fail_txt: "Failed，Click To Refresh",
            scaning_txt: "Smart Check Underway...",
            upLang: {
              cn: {
                //加载状态提示。
                LOADING: "Loading...",
                //等待滑动状态提示。
                SLIDE: "Please Slide to Verify",
                //验证通过状态提示。
                SUCCESS: "Verified Successfully",
                //验证失败触发拦截状态提示。
